# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:11
translate portuguese millspersonal1_d3a556ee:

    # pc "Do you have any close family?"
    pc "Tem alguma família próxima?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:13
translate portuguese millspersonal1_09575219:

    # bs "What kind of question is that? You want to know about my family? You want me to invite you over for Thanksgiving or something?"
    bs "Que tipo de pergunta é essa? Quer saber sobre a minha família? Quer que a convide para o Dia de Ação de Graças ou algo do género?"

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:14
translate portuguese millspersonal1_98e4d291:

    # pc "No. I'm sorry, Mrs. Mills, I was just making conversation."
    pc "Não. Desculpe, Sra. Mills, estava apenas a fazer conversa."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:16
translate portuguese millspersonal1_7006fe87:

    # bs "It's a sore spot. I don't really like talking about my lack of family."
    bs "É um ponto sensível. Não gosto muito de falar sobre a minha falta de família."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:17
translate portuguese millspersonal1_6c5191bf:

    # pc "Okay then, we don't have to talk about it."
    pc "Está bem, então não temos de falar sobre isso."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:18
translate portuguese millspersonal1_29ad1570:

    # bs "You're right. We don't."
    bs "Tem razão. Não temos."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:19
translate portuguese millspersonal1_6e9c55a7:

    # "We sit there for an awkward moment before she speaks up again."
    "Ficamos ali sentados num momento de constrangimento antes de ela voltar a falar."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:21
translate portuguese millspersonal1_4ddd6b78:

    # bs "Look, I'll tell you this. I've never been married, I don't have any children, and I cut my extended family off when they just kept calling asking me for money."
    bs "Olhe, vou dizer-lhe isto. Nunca me casei, não tenho filhos e cortei relações com a minha família alargada quando eles não paravam de me ligar a pedir dinheiro."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:22
translate portuguese millspersonal1_0d35df06:

    # pc "You're not married? But I've seen you wearing a wedding ring sometimes."
    pc "Não é casada? Mas já a vi a usar uma aliança às vezes."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:24
translate portuguese millspersonal1_efa8b66e:

    # bs "Yes, I wear that when I go to court. Juries tend to dislike female lawyers anyway, and an unmarried female lawyer is the scum of the earth in their eyes."
    bs "Sim, uso-a quando vou ao tribunal. Os júris tendem a não gostar de advogadas de qualquer forma, e uma advogada solteira é a escória da terra aos olhos deles."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:25
translate portuguese millspersonal1_e9793bcb:

    # pc "What? That's ridiculous."
    pc "O quê? Isso é ridículo."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:27
translate portuguese millspersonal1_b9fcc423:

    # bs "Yes it is, but it's true. Unmarried female lawyers tend to lose cases because one member of the jury or another just doesn't like them."
    bs "Sim, é, mas é verdade. As advogadas solteiras tendem a perder os casos porque um ou outro membro do júri simplesmente não gosta delas."

# game/Scenes/MrsMills/MillsConversation/millspersonal1.rpy:28
translate portuguese millspersonal1_0182d4e3:

    # bs "So I wear a ring. I call myself \"Mrs.\" Mills. It helps me win and I like to win."
    bs "Por isso uso uma aliança. Chamo-me a mim própria «Sra.» Mills. Ajuda-me a ganhar e eu gosto de ganhar."

